FT  04 JUN 92 / Rise in number of foreign tourists
the second-highest March figure ever. The total number of overseas visitors
in the first three months of the year was 3.2m, a 14 per cent increase on
the first quarter of last year, when tourism was hit by the Gulf war.
The visitors who came in the first quarter spent Pounds 1.3bn - also 14 per
cent up on the same period last year.
